column5: I'm looking for any information from people who have been there before. I already have their web-site, but I'm looking for opinions good and bad regarding the service, food, lodging. Thanks - JP

My company represents Birch Lake Lodge and we have had nothing but good reports about them. If you would like a copy of our inspection reports on this lodge or any others in that area, please feel free to ask and I can send a package to you on the 125 outfitters that we book for.Happy fishing.RichOutdoor ConnectionTemperance, MI
